{"tid":1512133,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)急需大量各種罷課文宣","createTime":"2019-08-27T18:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T16:41:55.000Z","uid":258571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8ec6975523f636ac0d97cf6b33e5ef5336db05","tid":1512133,"uid":258571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:10:21.000Z","msg":"嚟緊我間學校會罷課<br />\n諗住趁有啲學校暑假補課 周街貼文宣 派傳單 講罷課<br />\n但係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同同區傾咗92宣傳93先真罷<br />\n又咁啱呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家巿面啲罷課文宣全部都係寫92<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁小弟又冇乜藝術細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家可以幫手 揾到啲冇寫92罷嘅文宣<br />\n救下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(唔使好靚 入到眼就得)<br />\n(唔使有明確日期 有寫係罷課就得)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460cd64e66f9f180803ff4921a7485bcdecb8ef0","tid":1512133,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:28:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新post！